name: my 100th
description: You are buying history. My history. After so much frustrated attempts of make myself visible in the world of art, I made myself for those who really matter: those who like it.  Today I feel encouraged to continue, to push more and more the limits of what I know or can do, to bring ideas that cause sensations and that sharpen imaginations.  I wish you prosperity. As a thank you, I intend to continue challenging myself, transforming what I see to share.  Happy 100th, to us! jpg 4055x4096 px
